bilingual.source: The pirates are planning to kill them.
bilingual.target: 海盗们正计划杀死他们。

bilingual.source: The pirates plan to kill Jim and his friends.
bilingual.target: 海盗们计划杀死吉姆和他的朋友们。

bilingual.source: If they kill other animals, we also call them predators.
bilingual.target: 如果它们杀死其他动物，我们也称它们为捕食者。

bilingual.source: We wondered whether it would be better to kill the two whales.
bilingual.target: 我们想知道是否杀死这两头鲸鱼更好。

bilingual.source: They cut down trees and use chemicals that kill the plants that monarch caterpillars eat.
bilingual.target: 他们砍伐树木并使用杀死帝王蝶毛毛虫食用植物的化学品。

bilingual.source: Once a species is listed as endangered, it is against the law to harm or kill that animal.
bilingual.target: 一旦某个物种被列为濒危物种，伤害或杀死该动物就是违法的。
毒药可以杀死很多动物。

list.abstract: kill是英文单词，字面义为“杀死”，有动词、名词、形容词词性。IT行业引用后转义为“剔除”、“删除”等。在游戏中有“double kill”，“triple kill”一说，它代表连杀数。
说明：kill 送出一个特定的信号 (signal) 给行程 id 为 pid 的行程根据该信号而做特定的动作,若没有指定，预设是送出终止 (TERM) 的信号

yingyinNormal.en: Are those real? Real enough. But you can't kill anyone you're not supposed to.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些是真的吗？足够真了，但是不能用来杀死那些你不该杀死的人。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you insane? I mean Joey, is going to kill you, he's actually going to kill you dead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你疯了不成？乔伊会杀了你，他真的会把你杀死的。

yingyinNormal.en: Mum tries to protect the kingdom by giving son the key. I kill Mum, but fail to kill the son.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她为了保护这个国家把钥匙给了她儿子，我杀了妈妈，但是没杀死孩子。

yingyinNormal.en: So were they. They were gonna kill all of us. You don't know that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们也是，他们会把我们所有人都杀死，这你没法知道。

yingyinNormal.en: Can't kill you if you're already dead. Besides, I wasn't sure who to trust.
yingyinNormal.zh: 死掉的人没法再杀死他，另外我也不知道该相信谁。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't understand. You built this program. Why is it trying to kill us?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不明白，是你设计的这个程序，可它为何要杀死我们？

yingyinNormal.en: You wanna know how to kill a shadow? You just shine a little light on it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你想知道要怎么杀死影子吗？只需要照一点光就可以了。

yingyinNormal.en: You didn't kill her and chop her up, that's not what we're smelling, right?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你没有杀死她，然后碎尸吧，屋里的味道不是尸臭，对吧？

yingyinNormal.en: No, not yet. They'll kill Toothless. No, Astrid we have to think this through carefully.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还不行，他们会杀死没牙，我们得仔细地考虑清楚。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't understand. I cared for Theresa. Loved her. Why did you make me kill her?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不明白，我在乎特蕾莎，我爱她，你为什么让我杀死她？

yingyinNormal.en: And they have bones reinforced with naturally occurring carbon fiber. They are very hard to kill.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们的骨骼含有天生碳纤维，强壮坚硬极难杀死。

yingyinNormal.en: Let us not forget, that it was Girion, Lord of Dale, your ancestor, who failed to kill the beast.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不要忘了，吉利恩河谷城主，你的先人没能杀死那怪物。

yingyinNormal.en: I was a coward. I was weak. I wouldn't kill a dragon. You said wouldn't that time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是个懦夫，我太软弱，我不愿意杀死一只龙。你这次说"不愿意"。

yingyinNormal.en: When you get a virus, you get a fever. That's the human body raising its core temperature to kill the virus.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当你感染上病毒，你就会发烧。这是人体提高自己的体温来杀死病毒。

yingyinNormal.en: He wants to detonate that Seed in the biggest city and kill millions. He's gonna show the world, "Baby, I'm back."
yingyinNormal.zh: 在最大的城市引爆种子杀死数百万人！他会向全世界宣告"我回来了"。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, as impossible as it seems, the sloth has natural enemies that would like to harm or otherwise kill us.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的，表面看来虽然不可能，树懒有天敌可能伤害我们，甚至“杀死”我们。

yingyinNormal.en: But if you kill him, Katniss. If you end all of this... All those deaths, they mean something.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但如果你杀死了他，凯特尼斯，如果你结束了这一切...那些逝去的生命，就有意义了。

yingyinNormal.en: And that, out of jealousy and greed, Chad Bryson chose to kill his wife, Caroline, rather than risk being left with nothing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 出于嫉妒，出于贪婪，查德·布赖森宁愿杀死了他的妻子卡罗琳，也不愿一无所有地离开。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't want to kill Ultron. He's unique. And he's in pain. But that pain will roll over the earth, so he must be destroyed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我并不想杀死奥创，他是独特的，而且很痛苦，但他的痛苦会毁灭地球，所以他必须被摧毁。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, you and Monica have the same I'm-gonna-kill-you look. I can usually make it go away by kissing her. Get out.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道吗？你跟莫妮卡一样都有那种我想要杀死你的表情。我通常可以亲她一下就逃过一劫。滚出去。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

examination_example.sentence: Critics say the big companies use such deals to buy their most threatening potential competitors, as part of a "buy and <highlight>kill</highlight>" tactic to simply close them down.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 评论家们说，大公司利用此类交易来收购他们最具威胁性的潜在竞争对手，是“买杀”策略的一部分，此举能够简单地使这些公司倒闭。

examination_example.sentence: Already, since 2010, drought and insects have <highlight>killed</highlight> over 100 million trees in California, most of them in 2016 alone, and wildfires have burned hundreds of thousands of acres.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 自2010年以来，干旱和昆虫已经在加利福尼亚杀死了1亿多棵树，其中大部分树木在2016年集中死亡，野火已经烧毁了数十万英亩的土地。

examination_example.sentence: But postal special-interest groups seem to have <highlight>killed</highlight> it, at least in the House.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但邮政特殊利益集团似乎已经扼杀了它，至少在众议院是这样。
